@startuml
title Automation Framework - Module: yamlcase

left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor "Test Engineer" as User
artifact "case.yaml" as CaseYaml

package "yamlcase" {
  component "loader.py\nload_test_case()" as Loader
  component "_ensure_* helpers" as Guards
  component "_validate_stage_items()" as Validator
}

package "Dependencies" {
  component "PyYAML\nsafe_load()" as YamlLib
  component "core.models.TestCase" as TestCase
  component "runner.spec_registry\nbuild_registered_*_args()" as SpecRegistry
}

User --> CaseYaml
CaseYaml --> Loader : parse
Loader --> YamlLib : safe_load()
Loader --> Guards : normalize mappings /\nlists /\nnamed maps
Loader --> Validator : validate setup / steps /\nverification / teardown
Validator --> SpecRegistry : validate action/check args
Loader --> TestCase : build case model

note bottom of Validator
  yamlcase validates the scenario shape early,
  before runtime compilation begins.
end note

@enduml
